deas.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/04\/french-wedding-ideas-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/a>There is lots to know and actually legally getting married in France is not so straightforward but we are here to help you overcome every hurdle. : To get married either the bride or groom must have been resident in a in the same village, town or commune in France for a <strong>minimum of 40 consecutive days <\/strong>before they can get married. The application for the civil marriage may be made to the <em>Mairie<\/em> (Town Hall) once this residency has been achieved.<\/p>\n<p>There is lots more <a title=\"Information on arranging a wedding in France\" href=\"http:\/\/riviera.angloinfo.com\/countries\/france\/marriage.asp#1\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>wedding information in English<\/strong><\/a> here or you can email or call us up for a general chat about the ins and outs of getting married in France. Whatever happens we can help when it comes to arranging your <a title=\"Photos of a wedding in France\" href=\"https:\/\/plus.google.com\/u\/0\/photos\/116297197768817012242\/albums\/5684820619194861121\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>perfect wedding<\/strong><\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Arranging a wedding in France can be easy if you find the right wedding planner to help when it comes to arranging your dream wedding. That is where Red Radish&#8230; <a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/everything-you-need-to-know-about-arranging-a-wedding-in-france\/\"><span class=\"button button-outline button-dark\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> read more <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1833,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[11,25],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1817","post",